            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row body-content">
            <div>
                <h4>Upcoming items of interest</h4> 

                <ul class="list-group">
                    <li class="list-group-item"><a href='http://f3nation.com/2015/06/02/f3-dads-pre-blast/'>A51 Dads</a> - Saturdays in June<br />Beatty Park (down from the Siskey YMCA), 9:00-9:45am</li>
